Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:34.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  這不是半家的盤子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:34.14,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,（半家：鐮倉時代以後所成立的公卿門第中最下等的）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:35.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:36.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不  完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:39.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我這種身份的人配這種盤子已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,關於紫的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:45.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說拐走她的是個叫做紅香的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:47.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你從誰那聽來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:51.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,此話出自誰口如此重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:52.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:55.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,秘訣就是就算放著不管也會自然而然知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:57.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到的是真話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:01:58.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:02.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就算那是真話  也沒有任何問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:06.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫還會回到奧之院嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:11.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,秘訣就是就算放著不管也會自然而然有結果的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:39.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:46.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:48.91,op,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:10.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:13.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你半夜做噩夢了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:14.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那大概是呼嚕打得太響了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是  呼嚕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:23.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,先別說這個  我去學校真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人留在家裡能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:29.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別小瞧我  紅香不也說過這裡很安全嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,總之  不能到外面去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:32.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一出什麼事就馬上打我手機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:36.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼問題都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:40.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  絕對不能獨自一人離開五月雨莊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:41.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這個剛才已經吩咐過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這個房間和廁所活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:44.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要去學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我說  今晚真的能再見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:06.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  他也有按照自己的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:07.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙馬上就能習慣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是貓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:17.86,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}最近他老是說要開會什麼的很晚回家  說不定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:25.20,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}所以說  夫人您這麼對誰都不持戒心這點才會把你導向如此偏執的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:35.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:36.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,食物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:37.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:40.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,冰箱裡不是有嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,貓要吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:42.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,窗外有隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  別把它放進房裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:47.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,點心放在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:48.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,廚房的下面有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:49.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:57.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,過來  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,過來吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:00.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:11.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好難得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:13.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,平時你都很早到的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:17.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這個應該怎麼吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天早上遲到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:24.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  工作上瑣事太多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:28.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,當初是你自己決定上學和工作兼顧的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,關於九鳳院…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:33.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:36.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,也許這工作不適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,九鳳院來頭真的這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一無所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:44.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  與其說你不如說這是任務交給你的柔澤紅香的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:47.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這也不正代表她對我很信任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,應該只是人手不夠而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:53.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋也有其可利用之處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都只顧著逞強才老是失敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我說  冰箱裡有個袋子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:05.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,袋子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,超市的白色袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,超市是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:12.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,總之是白色的袋子  塑料的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:13.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡面有麵包  把它吃了也行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:17.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我不怎麼喜歡吃麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:18.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:21.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別為了這麼無聊的事三番四次地給我打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:26.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:28.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,飲料有果汁和茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:29.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯的時候可以喝果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:33.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊  隨你喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你在負責她的三餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是工作上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是個煩人的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:46.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,打開啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:50.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  有好好地吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一會  真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:00.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,又吃麵包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:07.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不再等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:12.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,一直吃這些東西可是會營養不良的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:13.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}在這裡  在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:22.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}媽媽  美紀一個人買回來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:23.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,買回來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:28.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,渾身無力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,上午上體育課真是太累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,明天也有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:32.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,上廁所  上廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:41.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:43.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是你這傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你是用「你這傢伙」打招呼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,把手放開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:48.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可以放開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別管了  快放開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:56.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才問你可以放開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這點小事沒什麼大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:02.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:05.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我是4號室的暗繪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:08.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,上廁所  上廁所  上廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:18.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,黑貓加上一身黑  你是魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:21.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我是惡婦人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,惡婦人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,把男人玩弄於鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:26.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,榨乾其錢財並優雅地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:28.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是惡婦人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:33.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:34.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,給女朋友打電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,新聞社的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:40.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:41.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:46.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我是家住6號室的武騰環  是真九郎君的女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:48.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你是女人我一看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:50.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我說  小紫今年幾歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:51.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,7歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:53.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,軟軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:54.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你和那個少年是什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎是紫的傭人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:05.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說小紫是真九郎君的主人囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:09.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是新手機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,之前的壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:19.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這顏色好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對了  這是小串珠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:23.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:27.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,繞成這個圓柱的形狀可是很難的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是買的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還配有圓珠筆很方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:40.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這顏色和真九郎的手機很配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:41.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這個真是買對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,過來過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:49.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好乖好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你的主人溫柔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:55.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  一般般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那個  帶子是不是太粗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強繫上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:05.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:10.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,最近你都沒去我家露個面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為工作很忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:20.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間有夕乃姐你說過想看的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:23.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對我不能談工作上的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:24.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:28.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,至少和夕乃姐在一起的時候我才想忘了那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:32.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因為  想說很多開心的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:36.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說起電影的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:37.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:42.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  看真九郎一直坐立不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:45.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我還擔心你在做什麼危險的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  是紫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒香煙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:10:59.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,香煙  香煙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:02.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,暗繪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有沒有一個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:07.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有個在看家的小女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚  說白了我連這是誰的手機都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:17.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的  你那邊沒有個小女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:17.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:18.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:19.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不在？到哪去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:23.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你有存香煙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  真的不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來大衛也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大衛呢  大衛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:36.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:42.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  是環姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:46.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}（您所撥的電話由於對方原因未能接通）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:47.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:55.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  你回來得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你  在幹嗎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:11:59.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒熱水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:02.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不會有熱水的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,接下去會越來越冷的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:05.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,手機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:06.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在電視機前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我打了多少次電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:10.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:12.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,看來電顯示的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:13.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在這房間裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎你給我弄熱水過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這水太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我想擦擦身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,渾身黏糊糊的  好不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:27.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就這麼睡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:33.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,去澡堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:37.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:38.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:44.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:47.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,她才7歲  能進男士浴池嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊  你原來有妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是暫住我這的表妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個可愛的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:57.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小真你原來喜歡這種類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了是我表妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:12:59.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大媽我嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是這樣就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:06.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:08.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小心滑倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:09.58,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,她還真是光明正大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,右邊癢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:15.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在下面點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:17.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:19.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得你一副不耐煩的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:20.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在家都是傭人幫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是你家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:26.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:27.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:28.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這泡沫是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:29.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:30.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,進到眼睛裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:32.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你睜著眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快沖一下  沖一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:35.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:38.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都說沖一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:42.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:45.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好熱  眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,的確熱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還有幾秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,2分30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:55.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:57.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:57.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:13:59.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:00.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,櫃檯的奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:01.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  到極限了  太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是正好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,把身體擦乾了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,擦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了頭髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  你別什麼事情都嘮嘮叨叨的煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:15.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:20.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:22.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,和紫相處得融洽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這工作要做到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子到底被誰盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:31.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,根據對方的不同我也能轉換下保護的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:34.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但這是事實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:38.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得厭煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:38.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:39.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,感到累嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:41.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:41.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要說的就這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:47.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我把錢匯到你那了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  生活費剛好吃緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:54.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還有件緊急的工作要你做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:57.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在的工作根本脫不開身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:01.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是要保護那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:05.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,等下會給你簡訊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的要我做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:08.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,一切拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅香大人  已經確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:18.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,請你先坐這輛車回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:19.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:23.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,她無大礙  已經入睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:24.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,以後要是親人間再有什麼糾紛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還要請你多多幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:30.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該給那個男人配個護衛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就遇上我  真是個幸運的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也是紅香大人出馬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能  那種程度而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:43.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  輪到高中生出場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你在嫉妒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:46.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒的是彌生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:49.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群傷腦筋的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:51.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對手可是九鳳院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你想接手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你在喝什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:05.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:07.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:08.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,付了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  那人拿給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不用給了  算大媽我請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:14.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.58,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你道過謝了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,道謝  為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:22.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼為什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:26.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我從浴室出來都有人給我準備好飲料的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了  這不是你家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:32.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛生氣  我說錯了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:34.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不道謝可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:34.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:35.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,很有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,作為傭人這是很正常的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:41.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為從浴室出來的我準備這些飲料是理所應當的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你  居然打我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:45.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快去道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是傭人拿牛奶給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:49.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你又打我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那位大媽不是傭人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼要給我牛奶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:54.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因為人家出於一片好意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:59.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那位大媽對你一片好意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:00.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要對我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:04.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大人對小孩親切點  有什麼可奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:07.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是我錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:08.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,接受別人好意的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,知道該怎麼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:13.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:18.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這次承蒙您多多照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:22.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我考慮不周  遲遲不曾道謝對此無可辯解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是十分慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:24.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:28.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:30.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,做得好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這時候  說「謝謝」就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:35.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這被子好薄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫家的被子肯定是又鬆又軟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  真九郎的被子好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:45.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎還是買床被子比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:50.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要是搞壞了身體  我可就頭疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:51.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛似乎手勢太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:17:59.58,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎說的是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了教導我才打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:09.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:14.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛雖然很疼  但並不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:15.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為大家都怕疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,跟真九郎一起也不差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:28.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是看到我的真面目可是要嚇一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,現在為止的真九郎是假的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:35.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是指每個人都有很多面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也遇到過很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:40.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:45.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來真九郎也能睡個好覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要比蓋件大衣服舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是紫的被子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我睡這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了我才買的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:56.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:19:00.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  這就不用擔心臭氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:02.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是喜歡這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候該道謝才對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:10.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦你為我考慮得這麼周到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我九鳳院紫對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫  剛才我教過你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:17.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,話可不是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍稍改裝一下  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:38.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以告辭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:41.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小哥你喜歡撲克牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是很會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:44.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:46.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以了  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:49.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我先走了  失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今天已經要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:54.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是正好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:55.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:59.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不想小題大做的要讓你把這變成賭場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:00.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過只是酒好喝可不盡興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:02.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要在這裡設賭局實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:03.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,給你面子才拜託你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:05.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:06.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有了孩子還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:09.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:11.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,負責攝影的那些傢伙還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:13.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在那公園太小了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,得根據你的答覆好好照顧一下才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是男孩  還是女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,請別這樣  求求你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:24.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哪個都行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:29.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  今天已經休業了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:31.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是來喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我是糾紛調解人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你是紅香小姐那的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣  還是個孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:43.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  這傢伙去拜託糾紛調解人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得這麼頑強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:48.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是個小鬼真是大失所望了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:49.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你還是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:51.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  可不好對付
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:55.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我是糾紛調解人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:59.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:02.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  這是我職責所在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:13.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:32.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:36.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:50.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:55.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:18.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  紫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:21.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:26.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮丈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:27.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮丈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.35,0:22:31.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅香小姐是個很值得依靠的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:32.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.71,0:22:35.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,您是這麼說的吧  蓮丈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.12,0:24:20.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,下集  紅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.80,0:24:23.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,虛假的面容
